Package: RMandrill
Title: This package is an api wrapper for R to use mandrill
Version: 0.1
Author: Evan Farrell <evandev@gastrograph.com>
Maintainer: Evan Farrell <evandev@gastrograph.com>
Description: This package is an api wrapper that sends emails using the
    mandrill platform
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    dplyr
Imports: 
    jsonlite,
    RCurl,
    httr,
    stringr,
    dplyr,
    base64
